title: Star Wars x Santa Cruz Skateboards
description:
The Santa Cruz team gets a little help introducing the New Star Wars collection of Decks and Cruzers from an all too familiar villain.

Santa Cruz Skateboards is honored to collaborate with Lucasfilm to present our Exclusive Special Edition Star Wars collection of Decks and Cruzers.

Known for some of the most iconic graphics in skateboarding history, Santa Cruz has created new, exclusive interpretations of your favorite characters.

Featuring Emmanuel Guzman, Justin Strubing, Sid Melvin, Shuriken Shannon, Josh Borden, Jason Jessee and Darth Vader.

Filmed on location in San Francisco CA.

Filmed and edited by Joe Perrin
Additional filming by Carson Lee 

Music: "Trigger" by Buck Buck Buck
